Package: DeepComBat
Title: DeepComBat Image Harmonization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fengling", "Hu", , "fengling.hu@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1081-5038"))
Maintainer: Fengling Hu <fengling.hu@pennmedicine.upenn.edu>
Description: Provides open-source code to apply the DeepComBat algorithm. Details of the method are described in more detail here: https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2023.04.24.537396v1. NeuroCombat dependency can be installed here: https://github.com/Jfortin1/neuroCombat_Rpackage.
Depends: torch, coro, neuroCombat, grDevices, graphics
